column5: My buddy, the Chief, has a personal web page about our Quetico activities, including helpful planning info and other pertinent links. For those of you who visit those waters, this might be helpful to you. If you've never gone to Quetico, there is enough info to get you started on the right track. Enjoy it!
Web page address was inadvertently ommited by me (senior moment).Check it out at: www.athenet.net/~chiefk
